==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Opposable
<hw>Op*pos"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Capable of being opposed or resisted.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Capable of being placed opposite something else;
<as>as, the thumb is <ex>opposable</ex> to the
forefinger</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Opposal</ent>⟦br⟧
